---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="catboyash - about">
	<body>
		<div class="flex w-max">
			<h1 class="font-bold text-6xl overflow-hidden border-solid border-r-[0.15em] border-purple whitespace-nowrap w-0 animate-typing">About Me</h1>
		</div>
		<p class="mb-4 mt-2">
			I've had an interest in coding after I first discovered the concept and I have been slowly teaching myself since then. I draw from time to time as well, and enjoy editing various things. I play in the front ensemble in marching band, you could consider me a band kid. You'll typically find me gaming or making stupid image edits in my free time.<br />Also, I hate graphic design.
		</p>
		<h2 class="text-purple text-2xl font-semibold">Games I Enjoy:</h2>
		<p class="mb-3">Some of my favorite games! <span class="text-purple">Purple</span> means I currently play this game.</p>
		<ul class="list-disc list-inside">
			<li><span class="text-purple">Terraria</span></li>
			<li><span class="text-purple">Lethal Company</span></li>
			<li><span class="text-purple">Splatoon 3</span></li>
			<li><span class="text-purple">Minecraft</span></li>
			<li><span class="text-purple">Geometry Dash</span></li>
			<li>Hollow Knight</li>
			<li>Celeste</li>
			<li>Everhood</li>
			<li>Phasmophobia</li>
			<li>Bloons TD 6</li>
		</ul>
	</body>
</Layout>